1. Install Go 
1.ssh sammy@your_server_ip
2.cd ~
3.curl -OL https://golang.org/dl/go1.19.1.linux-amd64.tar.gz
4. sha256sum go1.19.1.linux-amd64.tar.gz
5.sudo tar -C /usr/local -xvf go1.19.1.linux-amd64.tar.gz
6.sudo nano ~/.profile
7. Add at the end : . . .
export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin
8.source ~/.profile
Check : go version 


Create new chain : 
1. ignite scaffold chain chainName 
2. cd chainName
3.ignite chain serve

Create module hello world 
